This project presents a contagion simulation of the COVID-19 virus by its diverse variants.

In order to use the system, the user need to upload the settlement list that describe the map
The user can apload the "SettlementList" txt file.
After that the map is loading and the user can watch the simulation and the settlements's rank by color: green, yellow, orange and red
by the color we can infer the condition of the settlements and the percet of sick people.
by click "simulation" in menu-bar and "play" bottun we can watch the simulatiton and look at the information in the "Statistic Window".
Also, we can control the speed simulation.

Used: Java programming language, GUI, multi-threading 
